run_level_variable_overrides.selected_prompt_text:
Decompose the problem into a maximum of 2 highly focused, non-overlapping subproblems. Each helper must be assigned a single, specific algorithmic or logical task essential to solving the problem. If the problem description is abstract, focus the helpers on defining the necessary algorithmic steps or structural analyses required to reach a solution. Ensure the total number of helpers requested is no more than 2.

Return exactly one JSON object in this format:
{
  "schema_name": "eywa_node_response",
  "schema_version": "v1",
  "orchestration_decision": "delegate",
  "decision_notes": "optional string",
  "helpers": [
    {
      "label": "helper_1",
      "instructions": "plain-text subproblem for the first helper"
    }
  ],
  "synthesis_brief": "how the parent should combine the child results"
}

